overview: This is the Damn Yankees at Nakano Sun Plaza, Tokyo, Japan on January 20, 1993. Setlist: 01. Don't Tread On Me / 02. Damn Yankees / 03. Rock City / 04. Free-For-All (Ted Nugent song) / 05. This Side of Hell / 06. Where You Goin' Now / 07. Come Again / 08. Uprising / 09. Renegade (Styx cover) / 10. (You Can Still) Rock in America (Night Ranger cover) / 11. Coming of Age / 12. High Enough
title: Damn Yankees: Live In Japan
